**DIGITS(CNUM)*AS*CNUM,*********************************************************:             CSD027
         CNUM  AS CNUM,                                                         :             CSD027
  CCY,                                                                          :
  ACOD,                                                                         :
  ACSQ,                                                                         :
  CFSB,                                                                         :
  V_CUSTNAME.CUSTOMER                                                           :
  FROM ACCNTAB                                                                  :
**LEFT*JOIN*V_CUSTNAME*V_CUSTNAME*ON*BBCUST=DIGITS(CNUM)************************:             CSD027
  LEFT JOIN V_CUSTNAME V_CUSTNAME ON BBCUST=       CNUM                         :             CSD027
